  <brief_title>Ocytocine and Cerebral Activation in Relation With Attachement</brief_title>
  <acronym>OTACLA</acronym>
  <official_title>A Cross Over Randomized Controlled Trial of the Effect of Nasal Ocytocine on Cerebral Activations in Relation With Attachement in the General Population</official_title>
  <sponsors>
